OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLloyds Bank: Police        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwatchdog to examine alleged
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fleaks                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An investigation into allegations of   
OL,6, fraud against Lloyds Bank is being     
OL,7, examined by a police watchdog.         
OL,9,FAvon and Somerset Police has referred  
OL,10,Fitself to the Independent Office of    
OL,11,FPolice Conduct (IOPC) after claims that
OL,12,Finformation was leaked to the bank.    
OL,14,FIt relates to a long-running enquiry   
OL,15,Finto allegations of fraud at the Lloyds
OL,16,FRecoveries unit in Bristol.            
OL,18,FA police spokesperson confirmed it had 
OL,19,Fmade a mandatory referral to the IOPC  
OL,20,Ffollowing a complaint.                 
